name: Cruise Intervals #3
description:
Today's session consists of 3 x 12-minute cruise intervals. Cruise intervals are performed within Zone 4. However, each 12-minute interval is proceeded by a 30 second Zone 5 interval. 



However, we change the target power every minute from 92% to 97%. Focus on controlled breathing and pedalling at a cadence similar to your Time Trial cadence.
